  <entry>
    <title>MAC方法</title>
    <link href="https://fenglielie.github.io/learn/learn-inse-mac.html"/>
    <id>https://fenglielie.github.io/learn/learn-inse-mac.html</id>
    <published>2022-07-03T16:22:02.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-07-04T09:25:57.591Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;标记网格法(Marker-and-Cell
method，MAC)，是一种求解压力Poisson方程算法，最初被设计用于求解含自由面的不可压缩流动。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    <category term="learn" scheme="https://fenglielie.github.io/categories/learn/"/>
    
    
    <category term="inse" scheme="https://fenglielie.github.io/tags/inse/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>SIMPLE算法</title>
    <link href="https://fenglielie.github.io/learn/learn-inse-simple.html"/>
    <id>https://fenglielie.github.io/learn/learn-inse-simple.html</id>
    <published>2022-07-03T13:49:15.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-07-05T09:47:28.447Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;SIMPLE算法全称是压力耦合方程组的半隐式方法(Semi-Implicit Method for
Pressure Linked Equations),
作为经典的压力修正算法在Fluent等工业软件中被广泛应用。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    <category term="learn" scheme="https://fenglielie.github.io/categories/learn/"/>
    
    
    <category term="inse" scheme="https://fenglielie.github.io/tags/inse/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>涡量—流函数方法</title>
    <link href="https://fenglielie.github.io/learn/learn-inse-vortex.html"/>
    <id>https://fenglielie.github.io/learn/learn-inse-vortex.html</id>
    <published>2022-07-03T13:22:52.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-07-04T09:25:44.361Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;通过把原始变量(速度，压强)转化为导出变量(涡量，流函数)的方程组，可以避开处理压强时的困难，称为涡量-流函数方法。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    <category term="learn" scheme="https://fenglielie.github.io/categories/learn/"/>
    
    
    <category term="inse" scheme="https://fenglielie.github.io/tags/inse/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>投影法</title>
    <link href="https://fenglielie.github.io/learn/learn-inse-projection.html"/>
    <id>https://fenglielie.github.io/learn/learn-inse-projection.html</id>
    <published>2022-07-03T12:31:23.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-07-04T09:25:53.857Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;投影法也称为时间分裂法，分步法，按照思路分为两类：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;第一类基于N-S方程组的半离散格式，基于Helmholtz分解定理；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;第二类基于N-S方程组的全离散格式，采用近似算子分裂/近似矩阵分裂。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;下文只包括第一类投影法。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    <category term="learn" scheme="https://fenglielie.github.io/categories/learn/"/>
    
    
    <category term="inse" scheme="https://fenglielie.github.io/tags/inse/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
